{"tid":685044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴黎驅逐1700非法聚居難民　推土機出動鏟走帳幕","createTime":"2018-05-31T05:56:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T07:14:22.000Z","uid":75969,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"679283417484b984d1e0e67daeb91f9d411a4db3","tid":685044,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T05:56:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180531/photo/bknint-20180531100036579-0531_17011_001_01p.jpg?20180531100347\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180531%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180531100036579-0531_17011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180531100347&h=1bc6d980&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">工作人員清理現場。（法新社圖片）<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180531/photo/bknint-20180531100036579-0531_17011_001_02p.jpg?20180531100347\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180531%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180531100036579-0531_17011_001_02p.jpg%3F20180531100347&h=43d870a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">警員協助撤走難民。（法新社圖片）</span><br />\n<br />\n法國當局周三（30日）早上對首都最大難民非法聚居地展開驅逐行動，據報該處住有1700人。當局把難民分派到20個中心暫住，包括在首都城和周邊郊區，隨後再送往接待及檢查中心，等侯確認身份。<br />\n<br />\n內政部下令大巴黎區警署和首都警署，對巴黎19區北面城邊的難民聚居地開始驅逐行動。在警員協助下，該批主要來自非洲的難民先由巴士送往體育館，之後推土機出動移除帳幕，工作人員清理現場。在過去多月以來，大批非法移民在巴黎運河區自行搭起露營帳幕聚居，已引起附近一帶居民關注安全和衞生問題。<br />\n<br />\n內政部長哥倫布上周三（23日）下令非法難民撤離，當局自2015年起，已在全國進行超過30次同類行動，撤走超過28,000人。巴黎是最大非法移民聚居地，佔政治庇護申請人的四成，但遠遠超越首都能夠承受的接濟設施。<br />\n<br />\n駐法國記者呂靜儀報道<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180531/bknint-20180531100036579-0531_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180531%2Fbknint-20180531100036579-0531_17011_001.html&d=GnWKmyyN4rJLgsDKGmBCiJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=804da0ee\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180531/bknint-20180531100036579-0531_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5251240c007dc848038771235dd9e1401387d71d","tid":685044,"uid":37375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T06:59:19.000Z","msg":"當局把難民分派到20個中心暫住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3345edbba18d2d5abc1ec8eff1edf183df5c2ca1","tid":685044,"uid":51932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T07:01:12.000Z","msg":"法西斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46449eb3fb07b50223a8dbc59465e3a37bc58b86","tid":685044,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T07:02:02.000Z","msg":"喂個總統唔係好撚威的咩"},{"pid":"c36282b4e4b1cafcf12105062829c164e60a51fc","tid":685044,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T07:03:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"71a4eeef01a0b53fbc19307158b3b55798c3d6ea","tid":685044,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T07:06:18.000Z","msg":"集中營效率清理仲好啦"},{"pid":"73df6be08855af7f473088cef65f0f11ce718fc0","tid":685044,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T07:14:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}